member.example:
 The following example shows how to read the contents of a file by using the  method.
 
 using CancellationTokenSource tokenSource = new (TimeSpan.FromSeconds(1));
 using StreamReader reader = File.OpenText("existingfile.txt");

 Console.WriteLine(await reader.ReadToEndAsync(tokenSource.Token));

member.remarks:
If this method is canceled via , some data
that has been read from the current  but not stored (by the
